The visual identity is recorded in the *Brand Guide* and the *Design System*. The primary brand colour is **{{TODO_PRIMARY_HEX}}**; the secondary palette and the type system are in the *Brand Guide*.

No team member should be guessing what a brand colour or a heading font is. If the answer is not in the *Brand Guide*, the *Brand Guide* is wrong, and the fix is to update the *Brand Guide*.

